description.@value: ヘディンのペルシア踏査旅行記の第2巻。カビール沙漠横断の旅の記録の他、マルコ・ポーロの通った道についての考察、ペルシアの沙漠や盆地、気候変化などの考察を含む。

Volume 2 of Hedin’s Persia expedition travel record. In addition to an account of crossing the Kavir Desert, the work discusses Marco Polo’s route, climate change and the basins and deserts of the region.

value.@value: with 308 Illustrations from Photographs, Watercolour Sketches, and Drawings by the Author and 2 Maps
